pan class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Iff\">↔</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.GradingCompliant\">GradingCompliant</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs'</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.congr\">congr</a> <span class=\"fn\">⋯</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.gradingCompliant_congr","kind":"theorem","line":477,"name":"WickContraction.gradingCompliant_congr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L477-L481"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.GradingCompliant\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">GradingCompliant</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, `φs` a list of `𝓕.FieldOp` and a Wick contraction\n`φsΛ` of `φs`, the Wick contraction `φsΛ` is said to be `GradingCompliant` if\nfor every pair in `φsΛ` the contracted fields are either both `fermionic` or both `bosonic`.\nIn other words, in a `GradingCompliant` Wick contraction if\nno contracted pairs occur between `fermionic` and `bosonic` fields. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.GradingCompliant","kind":"def","line":469,"name":"WickContraction.GradingCompliant","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L469-L475"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction.prod_finset_eq_mul_fst_snd\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">prod_finset_eq_mul_fst_snd</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">M</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\">n</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">c</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span c